# naql demo
Output demo.gif
Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1100
Set Height 650
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 25ms
Set Padding 16

Hide
Type "source .venv/bin/activate && clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Sleep 300ms
Type "naql formats"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "naql inspect ~/Projects/Aamil/training/fused/combined_cf_50_4bit"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "naql arabic ~/Projects/Aamil/training/fused/combined_cf_50_4bit"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

Sleep 2s
